迈克尔·道格拉斯 (Michael Douglas) 不喜欢被称为“尼波宝宝”：“谁不尝试帮助自己的儿子呢？” https://www.nme.com/news/film/michael-douglas-doesnt-take-kindly-to-being- Called-a-nepo-baby-who-doesnt-try-to-help-his-son- 3819940？ut m_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=迈克尔-道格拉斯-不善意地对待被称为尼波婴儿的人，他不尝试帮助他的儿子Elizabeth AubreySat, 07 Dec 2024 10:22:23 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3819940 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="迈克尔·道格拉斯" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位演员还公开了他与 2020 年去世的父亲柯克·道格拉斯 (Kirk Douglas) 的关系</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/michael-douglas-doesnt-take-kindly-to-being-called-a-nepo-baby-who-doesnt-try-to-help-his-son-3819940">迈克尔·道格拉斯 (Michael Douglas) 的帖子不喜欢被称为“尼波宝宝”：“谁不尝试帮助自己的儿子呢？”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="迈克尔·道格拉斯" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，演员迈克尔·道格拉斯（Michael Douglas）对被称为“尼波宝宝”很不高兴，他说：“谁不尝试帮助自己的儿子呢？”</p><p>周五（12 月 6 日），道格拉斯在沙特阿拉伯吉达举行的红海电影节上发表讲话，谈到在父亲柯克的阴影下在好莱坞成为一名演员是多么具有挑战性，柯克被广泛认为是一位好莱坞演员。好莱坞最伟大的演员之一。他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/kirk-douglas-actor-dead-2605638">于 2020 年去世，享年 103 岁。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/michael-douglas-silicon-valley-hollywood-1236079367/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>《好莱坞报道》</i></a>写道，道格拉斯不喜欢“好莱坞尼波宝宝”的标签，但接着表示，如果有能力，任何父亲都会帮助他们的儿子。</p><p>他解释说：“我不认识任何从事任何行业的父亲，无论是水管工、承包商还是木匠，他都会尽力帮助他的儿子加入他的行列。我也是尼波宝宝，你知道吗？所以事情就是这样，”他补充道。</p><p>他接着解释了他的父亲柯克如何帮助他监制米洛斯·福尔曼的<i>《飞越疯人院》，</i>该片最终赢得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscar">奥斯卡</a>最佳影片奖。</p><p>道格拉斯解释了柯克如何<i>在 1962 年获得将《飞越疯人院》</i>改编成百老汇舞台剧和电影的权利。道格拉斯随后表示，他必须说服父亲允许他制作改编的电影。</p><p> “我有点冲动地说，‘让我来运行它，’道格拉斯解释道，然后详细说明了他如何最终获得父亲的许可来运行该项目。 </p><figure id="attachment_3819951" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3819951" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3819951" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-with-wife-Catherine-Zeta-Jones-CREDIT-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="迈克尔·道格拉斯与妻子凯瑟琳·泽塔·琼斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-with-wife-Catherine-Zeta-Jones-CREDIT-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-with-wife-Catherine-Zeta-Jones-CREDIT-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-with-wife-Catherine-Zeta-Jones-CREDIT-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-with-wife-Catherine-Zeta-Jones-CREDIT-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-with-wife-Catherine-Zeta-Jones-CREDIT-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Michael-Douglas-with-wife-Catherine-Zeta-Jones-CREDIT-Photo-by-Arnold-Jerocki_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3819951" class="wp-caption-text">迈克尔·道格拉斯和妻子凯瑟琳·泽塔·琼斯 – 图片来源：Arnold Jerocki/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “当你开始一个项目时，有一个风险因素也会让你感到紧张。但紧张只是你职业生涯、工作的一部分，”他继续说道。</p><p>在他的整个职业生涯中，道格拉斯赢得了无数荣誉，包括两项奥斯卡金像奖、五项金球奖和一项黄金时段艾美奖。</p><p>他因在<i>《华尔街》</i> 、 <i>《致命诱惑》</i> 、 <i>《本能》、《堕落》</i>和<i>《神奇男孩》等电影中的表演而受到好评。</i>因在 HBO 电影<i>《烛台背后》</i>中与马特·达蒙 (Matt Damon) 合作饰演钢琴家利伯拉斯 (Liberace)，他获得了黄金时段艾美奖迷你剧或电影最佳男主角奖。</p><p>从那时起，他就喜欢上<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag.Netflix">Netflix</a>喜剧<i>《科明斯基方法》</i> ，甚至在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/marvel-cinematic-universe">漫威电影宇宙</a>中饰演<i>《蚁人》</i>中的汉克·皮姆。</p><p>道格拉斯还于 2010 年被诊断出患有第四期喉癌，经过治疗后于 2013 年痊愈。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/michael-douglas-doesnt-take-kindly-to-being-called-a-nepo-baby-who-doesnt-try-to-help-his-son-3819940">迈克尔·道格拉斯 (Michael Douglas) 的帖子不喜欢被称为“尼波宝宝”：“谁不尝试帮助自己的儿子呢？”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
